docs {
  ## Description
  Soft-delete an ephemeris, mark ephemeris in DB as is_active = False, allowing later restoration.
  
  ## User Roles
  |User Role          |Permissions                                                      |
  |-------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------|
  |Superuser          |Can delete all ephemeris.                                        |
  |Analyst            |Can delete all ephemeris.                                        |
  |Operator           |Can delete ephemeris in his organization.                        |
  |Organization Admin |Can delete ephemeris in his organization.                        |
  |Everyone else      |Can't delete any ephemeris.                                      |
}
